frames.caption: A massive serpent is coiled around the Eiffel Tower, its body draped ominously over the iconic structure. Below, a solitary figure stands, gazing up at the surreal scene, surrounded by a desolate urban landscape.
frames.description: The scene depicts a fantastical and eerie setting where a giant snake is entwined around the Eiffel Tower, creating a sense of tension and wonder. The atmosphere is bleak, with overcast skies and barren trees, enhancing the dramatic and mysterious tone.
